{"tid":1626912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香 港 人 係 最 善 忘 既 民 族","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T18:52:05.000Z","uid":50502,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"49c167b3d4e98a1f15c4fd07dd74ecd2e1bea029","tid":1626912,"uid":50502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:36:44.000Z","msg":"睇完個post: 有幾樣嘢唔值得爆，唔值得大肆裝修，希望可以成為大家共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625713\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625713</a><br />\n<br />\n有兩千正評<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地係咪善忘大愛到傻撚左</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n上個月手捉跳下閘 痴下memo 就比藍絲打 cool頸 拎刀斬<br />\n今日同我講藍絲出黎挑釁都唔好出手<br />\n<br />\n上個月所有不合作運動被破解 而家發現紅藍店呢個春袋 手足開始有一絲希望 , 然後而家吹風話有賊偷野 就叫人唔好攪 <br />\n如果一早吹風話一反抗解放軍就落黎屠城 場運動係咪唔洗開始？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n交通燈就真係唔好攪 陸上交通麻煩港豬自然去搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"cdfbc9b03123867bd72d4b9bfd173be840be6277","tid":1626912,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"b927e6ecad934c01877a82d724162df7ebbb0bae","tid":1626912,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:41:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a13761ce074fdfc4af379042057a07ad55c2636b","tid":1626912,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘721 831</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6n36Dtt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6n36Dtt.jpg&h=43d3a2f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvbTitt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvbTitt.jpg&h=5482f8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdGLT1O.jp